<!-- Back-button — spec card render
     Source spec: ds-architect-agent/children/components/navigation.md#back-button -->
<div class="dst-component-card">
  <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between mb-2">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900">Back-button</h3>
    <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 font-mono">3 variants · 3 sizes · 4 states</p>
  </div>
  <p class="dst-component-intro">Back navigation primitive — chevron-left + optional label.</p>

  <div class="dst-spec-row">
    <span class="dst-spec-label">Variants</span>
    <div class="dst-spec-values">
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-variant">icon · chevron only</span>
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-variant">labeled · chevron + "Back"</span>
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-variant">context · previous page name</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="dst-spec-row">
    <span class="dst-spec-label">Sizes</span>
    <div class="dst-spec-values">
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-size">sm · 32px</span>
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-size">md · 40px</span>
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-size">lg · 48px</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="dst-spec-row">
    <span class="dst-spec-label">States</span>
    <div class="dst-spec-values">
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-state">idle</span>
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-state">hover</span>
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-state">focus</span>
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-state">pressed</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="dst-spec-note"><strong>Structure:</strong> chevron-left (leading edge, fixed) + (optional) label. <strong>Behavior:</strong> triggers <code>router.back()</code> or equivalent. Context variant pulls previous route name from router state — falls back to "Back" if unavailable.</div>
</div>
